author: Minecraft
description:
Uncover the story of The Biome That Broke Minecraft as Cory Scheviak and Jens Bergensten share behind-the-scenes developer secrets! Hear about their guiding principles, how they balance risk and reward, and what they consider the perfect amount of destruction – all while the Narrator does his best to wreak havoc on the Overworld.

Kingdom Survival map provided by Blockception
title: THE BIOME THAT BROKE MINECRAFT
